Package: libasound2
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Replaces: alsalib0.3.0, alsalib0.3.2, alsalib
Conflicts: alsalib0.1.3, alsalib0.3.0, alsalib0.3.2, alsalib
Description: ALSA library
 This package contains the binaries of alsa-lib,
 the ALSA library.
 .
 ALSA is the Advanced Linux Sound Architecture.

Package: libasound2-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libc6-dev | libc-dev, libasound2 (= ${Source-Version})
Suggests: libasound2-doc
Provides: alsalib-dev
Replaces: alsalib0.3.0-dev, alsalib0.3.2-dev, libasound0 (<= 0.4.1-2), libasound2 (<< 0.9.0rc7-2)
Conflicts: alsalib-dev
Description: ALSA library development files
 This package contains files required for developing software
 that makes use of alsa-lib, the ALSA library.
 .
 ALSA is the Advanced Linux Sound Architecture.

Package: libasound2-plugins
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, libasound2 (= ${Source-Version})
Description: ALSA library plugins
 This package contains plugins for the ALSA library that not
 included in the main libasound2 package.
 .
 Currently only the JACK plugin is included.
 .
 ALSA is the Advanced Linux Sound Architecture.

